name: Fish Homecoming
description:
Help mama fish get to her babies. But be careful. Caves can be tricky to maneuver. How fast can you reach them?

Press 'Right' to speed up and 'Left' to slow down.
Press 'Up' to go up and 'Down' to go down.

Press 'P' in game to open Pause menu.
Press 'M' anywhere to stop the music. You can change game volume in options.

It can take few seconds of black screen before it loads.
